    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We tried to-- so I approached him, and he says, you know by now that he has it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He goes, back in Poland, the way the cause was, it was [? untrustworthy ?] Jewish men.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
