      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "His daughter was-- it was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was there one worker who had to sign, the documents that the Jewish people received it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] some-- everything was conserved a very good, small-- from-- [NON-ENGLISH]",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] not like a prescription, medication.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the German take the good one, and probably leave in the supply room, even the bad one.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this time, he was sure that the war was right around the corner because Russia had been sending in front of the-- on the other side of Vistula.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he decided to run away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To bring everything to Schindler.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Schindler did give us some of the small sometimes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But in Czechoslovakia, I approached him and asked if he has a vitamin C.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And he told me, yes, I can give it to you, but you have to keep it in your hand.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they have to open it right in front of you and inject you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Otherwise, they would say, you could put in water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They give me [INAUDIBLE] of the injection.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And do you believe, that in one week, it started healing, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The wound was completely cured.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
